data.description: Spacious house, country living, close to town, LOTS of parking, on an acre of land with a 24x30 shop just waiting for all your toys and projects! (Shop is on a slab) 4BD/2BA+office, split floor plan, big primary bedroom with a oversized walk in closet. One of the bedrooms on the other end of the house is big enough to be a 2nd primary bedroom or use this space however you see fit, the possibilities are endless! Kitchen has stainless steel appliances and the refrigerator will stay. In the back yard there is a huge dog run for your pets to get all of the exercise they need and a covered area for shade when they need it. Good size deck for entertaining. Carport has a very good size storage area that exits to back yard. Roof New April 2023, HW Heater 2018  (Agents see showing & agent remarks)
